Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.21,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.21,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們始終踱步於境界線之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.93,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.69,0:01:14.93,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:17.55,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一，二，三，四...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:20.49,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:20.49,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都一樣
