Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.03,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.03,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆因此境風景獨好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:46.53,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない　でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:46.53,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛 or 盾？ 不想認輸 可是又不願受傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って　確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:49.52,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先挑一樣在手中仔細掂量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.72,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.72,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是發現再要反悔為時已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:57.17,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:57.17,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選的是哪邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.95,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.95,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思念是枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  追悔莫及的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:05.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:05.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  溫柔是弱點
